---
title: Creamy Garlic Salmon and Shrimp Penne with Spinach and Parmesan
description: This one's for those garlic lovers out there! Creamy penne topped with salmon and shrimp, stirred with spinach and finished with Parmesan makes for a decadent and memorable dinner!
